data.title: 2001-02 UD INSPIRATIONS SAMUEL DALEMBERT #124 MOSES MALONE JERSEY RELIC 474/1500
data.meta_description: This is a rare 2001-02 UD Inspirations Samuel Dalembert #124 Moses Malone Jersey Relic 474/1500 trading card. The card features basketball legends Stephen Curry and Michael Jordan and is made of high-quality card stock material. It is an original and licensed print manufactured by Upper Deck and includes a relic parallel/variety. The jersey used in the making of this card is from the Washington Wizards and Golden State Warriors teams. The card is ungraded and is perfect for any avid sports trading card collector.
